      "coarse": "arg_fact",
      "fine": "none",
      "asp": "none",
      "pol": "none"
    },
    {
      "review_id": "HJgjezT1Tm",
      "sentence_index": 4,
      "text": "In addition to the extensive experimentation on different settings showing performance improvements, the authors also present an ablation study, that shows the impact of the method when applied to different layers.",
